{"tid":1020216,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙 拿 下 葬 細 節 曝 光","createTime":"2019-02-13T12:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T14:51:06.000Z","uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"42b9c93bc1ed6216f60db83fe7c47184b05ca979","tid":1020216,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T12:51:14.000Z","msg":"source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=24580785766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D24580785766&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEbHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=45d24b6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=24580785766</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEbHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=083c03bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】卡迪夫城新援伊美利安奴沙拿在空難中喪命，遺體將於周五從英國送返家鄉阿根廷，更多下葬細節隨之曝光。<br />\n<br />\n28歲阿根廷前鋒伊美利安奴沙拿（Emiliano Sala）遺體運抵阿根廷後，會經6小時車程回到家鄉普羅格雷索，時間估計是周五晚上。 <br />\n<br />\n周六，守靈將設於沙拿兒時球會聖馬田的健身中心內，同時，之前出發到威爾斯的沙拿母親Mercedes和妹妹Romina，也會回到當地與其父Horacio會合。<br />\n<br />\n聖馬田主席列比路表示：「我們周六會用數小時，跟他說再永別。」沙拿在這兒效力至15歲，主席打算把主場命名為Estadio Emiliano Sala。<br />\n<br />\n卡城班主陳志遠早前主動提出願意支付將沙拿遺體送回阿根廷的一切費用。較早前，驗屍官從死因調查中確定了致命原因是頭部及胸部嚴重受傷。<br />\n<br />\n沙拿於上月由南特加盟卡迪夫城，1月21日晚由法國飛赴卡迪夫時，所乘坐的小型飛機在英倫海峽失蹤，經10多日來的打撈，終於尋獲遺體，機師伊保臣仍然下落不明。"},{"pid":"133a8dd4bd0b0762b109d0418f40368b49aa5009","tid":1020216,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42b9c93bc1ed6216f60db83fe7c47184b05ca979","tid":1020216,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T12:51:14.000Z","msg":"source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://spor